data.value: TK TAKOYAKI’s principal products are (1) Takoyaki and (2) Red Gulaman, while an optional product (3) Takoyaki Rice is also made available by the trademark. Takoyaki is prepared using two cooking sticks and a hollowed cast ironed plate exclusively made for cooking takoyaki. The ingredients are primarily batter made from our very own premix and fresh eggs, and stuffing ingredients comprised of cabbage, carrots and squid.
